metadata.name: Air Element
metadata.description: The Air element, your initiation into the BadDogs universe! As the foundational element and the sole one to be minted, Air embodies adaptability, swiftness, and receptivity, setting the stage for your BadDogs adventure. Possession of the Air Element automatically grants you access to all Air token raffles, featuring a majority of the remaining Genesis BadDogs and exclusive merchandise giveaways.
